sequenceDiagram
    participant User as Service Manager/Representative
    participant Dashboard as Service 360 React Dashboard
    participant SalesforceAPI as Salesforce API
    participant Database as Salesforce Database

    User->>Dashboard: Access Dashboard
    Dashboard->>SalesforceAPI: Request User Permissions
    SalesforceAPI-->>Dashboard: Validate Access Rights

    Dashboard->>Database: Fetch Urgent Cases
    Database-->>Dashboard: Return Urgent Cases Data
    Dashboard->>Dashboard: Process and Visualize Urgent Cases

    Dashboard->>Database: Retrieve Red Accounts
    Database-->>Dashboard: Return Red Accounts Data
    Dashboard->>Dashboard: Analyze Account Health Metrics

    User->>Dashboard: Select Time Frame Filter
    Dashboard->>Database: Query Cases for Selected Period
    Database-->>Dashboard: Return Time-Filtered Cases
    Dashboard->>Dashboard: Update Trend Visualizations

    User->>Dashboard: Drill Down on Specific Case/Account
    Dashboard->>SalesforceAPI: Request Detailed Record Information
    SalesforceAPI->>Database: Fetch Specific Record Details
    Database-->>SalesforceAPI: Return Record Data
    SalesforceAPI-->>Dashboard: Provide Detailed Information
    Dashboard->>User: Display Detailed View